channel.title: Wanting to Start a Developement Team
channel.description:
[center]Hello, my name is Tehpk. I am looking to start a developement team. I have been coding for some time now, and i would like to start a developement team for a server that could potentionally get over 1k players. I have a Quad Core 6G of ram vps online 24/7, I have Resources Including Funding for the project, Will have a .com/.net/.org Domain, Would like to have a webclient. The funding will Include Advertising the server to the extreme, and giving the developement team the ability to earn some real life cash, through paypal. If anyone is interested, please post here or send me a message. Please have some good 317+ coding experience. Thanks.
~Tehpk[/center]
